Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke karuwa cikin sauri a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da United Kingdom, daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Abubuwan da suka faru na cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) sun nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa yana da bambanci tsakanin ƙasashe, annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa na gaggawa ya kamata su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya tare da COVID-19 waɗanda za su buƙaci kulawar kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawar gaggawa.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an bayar da rahoton wani tarin cututtukan huhu na rashin sani a Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa mai haddasa cutar shine sabon coronavirus wanda yanzu ake kira coronavirus acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ya zuwa yanzu an tabbatar da cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, watau kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14% na lokuta, COVID-19 yana ci gaba zuwa mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawar asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6% na lokuta ke da mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke cikin asibiti saboda COVID-19 kusan kashi 4 ne.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin haɗuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta waɗannan ƙasashe da Lardin Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ta sami ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa da kuma yanayin cutar ta COVID-19 a duk duniya a halin yanzu bisa ga yanayin ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbataccen yanayin COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in uku da aka tabbatar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin waɗanda suka dawo daga Wuhan, Lardin Hubei, China.
Zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'ar COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da United Kingdom (UK), wanda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kuma haɗa da wannan kwanan wata, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samu yawan adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana samun adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, ana sabunta su kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, tare da kwatanta bayanan da Italiya.
A matsayin mai wakiltar yaduwar cutar COVID-19, mun lissafa yawan adadin cututtukan COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, saboda haka muna la'akari da yanayin yanayin COVID-19, a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin cututtukan da aka ruwaito ga kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da adadin adadin cututtukan Italiya na lokacin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin da ake samu na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya yana bin yanayin da ke cikin Lardin Hubei (China) (Hadisin 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK baki ɗaya, yawan haɗarin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Ƙarin bayani).
Wannan galibi ana haifar da saurin ƙaruwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya suna nuna irin wannan ci gaban haɓakar abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 (Ƙarin bayani).
Figure 2 ya nuna yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19, a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK dangane da waɗanda ke Italiya a lokacin Janairu 31 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Ya jaddada cewa, a ranar 15 ga Maris da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, sauran ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin adadin shari'o'in kamar Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna karuwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da UK.
Hanyoyin da aka lura na haɗuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana yaduwa a daidai wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin amsar lafiyar jama'a ta ƙasa da ma'anar shari'ar na iya bambanta a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ladabi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda dole ne a gwada su don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin biyo baya.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da raka'a kulawa mai tsanani a yankin sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai kan karɓar COVID-19 a asibiti da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa na gaggawa a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Koyaya, dole ne a tattara bayanan a cikin tsari don tallafawa bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ya mai da hankali kan yawan adadin rahotannin da aka bayar da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Binciken da aka gudanar a 2010-11 ya nuna bambancin bambancin da ke cikin wadatar gadaje na kulawa da kulawa a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a kowace mazauna 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasar tana da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa da kulawa da kulawa da hankali ga kowane mazauna 100,000 a 201011).
Yanayin samfurin da ya shafi ƙarancin ƙarfin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da UK na yaduwar COVID-19 da aka shigar da asibiti wanda ke da alaƙa da > 90% haɗarin wucewa da ƙarfin gadajen kulawa, an samar da su a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ƙimar haɗarin gaggawa game da COVID-19 ta ECDC.
Ganin cewa har yanzu an samar da ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa na musamman galibi suna aiki da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da shari'o'i da gadajen kulawa a cikin Tatanama don rukunin yanki na ƙididdigar 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa dole ne su kasance a shirye don yanayin yaduwar al'umma na SARS-CoV-2 da karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawar kiwon lafiya, musamman kulawar gaggawa, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka jaddada a cikin sabon kimantawa na haɗarin ECDC, hanzari, aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanya yana da mahimmanci don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauyawa daga tsarin hanawa zuwa ragewa, saboda tsammanin saurin ƙaruwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita martani idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
Har ila yau, binciken haɗarin gaggawa ya lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe za su iya ci gaba da haɓaka ƙoƙarin sarrafawa don rage saurin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya gaza, yana yiwuwa sauran tsarin kiwon lafiyar EU/EEA na iya fuskantar karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Barkewar cutar Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ke haifar da mummunar cutar cututtukan numfashi (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ya zuwa yanzu ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 kuma ya kamu da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, wanda ya haifar da bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar dai kwayar cutar ta SARS-CoV, wacce ta haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yaduwa daga barbashi kuma yana haifar da irin wannan alamun ta hanyar irin wannan hanyar.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙananan cututtuka da mutuwar fiye da SARS amma yana da sauƙin kamuwa da cutar kuma yana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
Domin yawan littattafai da ake bugawa game da wannan cuta, wannan talifin ya yi ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da wannan cibiyar bincike.
Za mu tattauna game da ilimin annoba, ilimin cututtuka, ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar da kuma kawar da wannan cuta mai barazana.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairun 2020 ya zama abin tunawa ga Sinawa da ba za su taɓa mantawa da shi ba yayin da aka tilasta musu su zauna a gida a lokacin hutu da kuma makonni bayan haka saboda barkewar cutar kwayar cutar.
Kwayar cutar tana da kama da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi (SARS) a shekara ta 2003; saboda haka, an kira ta SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu 2020 kuma an kira cutar da ke da alaƙa da cutar CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Wannan annobar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China kuma nan take ta bazu ko'ina cikin ƙasar da kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya.
Ya zuwa ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da sama da mutane 80,000 da aka tabbatar da cutar COVID-19, tare da an bar sama da mutane 40,000 da su koma gida kuma sama da mutane 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "magabcin jama'a ne na 1" kuma yana da yuwuwar zama mafi ƙarfi fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga takardu sama da 2000 game da COVID-19 gami da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin ilmin halitta, ganewar asali da magani tun lokacin da aka fara bayar da rahoto a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 wanda ya ƙayyade jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga wasu marasa lafiya.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon kuma saurin girma batun.
Idan ya dace, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da wata cuta da ke haifar da CoV, cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, wanda ya ɓarke a cikin 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka sani game da rigakafi da kuma tsinkayar cutar da kuma wasu tambayoyi masu muhimmanci.
CoVs a al'adance ana ɗaukar su a matsayin ƙwayoyin cuta marasa haɗari ga mutane, yawanci suna haifar da kusan 15% na mura mai yawa 4.
Koyaya, a wannan karni, mun sami CoVs na mutum masu cutarwa sau biyu, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka haifar da barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar barkewar cutar a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabiya a 2012, kuma nan ba da daɗewa ba suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe da yawa tare da mummunan yanayin rashin lafiya da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine annobar CoV ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam da aka rubuta.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a Figure 1.1, an fara bayar da rahoton tarin fuka-fukan da ba a san asalin su ba daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019 ga Hukumar Kiwon Lafiyar Kasa ta kasar Sin.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an fitar da kwayar cutar.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020 ne aka samu rahoton mutuwar mutum na farko daga Wuhan.
A halin yanzu, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa, larduna da ƙasashe maƙwabta.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an ba da rahoton kamuwa da cuta a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya, wanda ke nuna cewa kamuwa da cutar ɗan adam ga ɗan adam na iya faruwa.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, an sanya dokar hana fita a birnin Wuhan tare da dakatar da duk ayyukan sufuri na jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga Janairu, binciken farko na asibiti game da cutar ya ba da rahoton cewa, daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da aka tabbatar da cutar, 21 ne kawai suka yi hulɗa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku ta Wuhan wanda ake ganin asalin cutar daga asalin dabbobi ne da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiya a duniya.
A lokacin wannan rahoton, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin China da kusan wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya (Hoto (Hoto 2).2).
Ganin yadda lamarin ke ci gaba cikin sauri, ba a san iyakar cutar ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, binciken cibiyoyi da yawa na marasa lafiya 8,866 ciki har da 4,021 masu cutar COVID-19 da aka tabbatar sun ba da ƙarin bayani game da annobar kamar haka (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yana kamuwa da marasa lafiya na kowane zamani, amma yawanci suna tsakanin shekaru 30-65.
Kusan rabin (47.7%) na marasa lafiyar da ke dauke da cutar sun haura shekaru 50, kaɗan ne a ƙarƙashin shekaru 20 kuma mutane 14 ne kawai ke dauke da cutar da shekarunsu suka kai 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yana kamuwa da maza da yawa (0.31/100,000) fiye da mata (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yana ci gaba a cikin rukuni da yawa a cikin da ke kewaye da Hubei.
COVID-19 yana ɗaukar matsakaicin kwanaki 5 (2-9) daga farawa zuwa ganewar asali.
Matsakaicin lokacin da aka yi amfani da shi shine kwanaki 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Matsakaicin lokaci daga farawa zuwa mutuwa shine kwanaki 9.5 (4.8-13).
Ƙididdigar yawan haifuwa (R0) shine 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), kuma RO mai daidaitawa shine 2.23-4.82.
Yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar ya karu sosai kafin ranar 23 ga Janairun 2020, wanda ya yi daidai da lokacin motsi mai yawa kafin bikin bazara a China.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya tare da tabbatar da shari'ar shine 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), kuma daidaitaccen mutuwar ga dukkan marasa lafiya shine 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Manyan abubuwan bincike guda uku don COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (≥60) da kuma cutar huhu mai tsanani.
CoVs suna cikin ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta masu girma da ke ɗauke da RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya raba kwayar cutar zuwa jinsuna huɗu, cth., alpha, beta, gamma, da delta, daga cikin dukkanin alpha- da beta-CoVs da aka sani suna kamuwa da mutane.
Spike (S) glycoprotein surface yana ɗaure ga masu karɓar salula na ƙwayoyin cuta masu canza angiotensin 2 (ACE2) da dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoVs, sannan haɗuwa da membrane yana faruwa.
Ana sakin kwayar cutar RNA zuwa cikin cytoplasm; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar, RNA ta kwayar halitta tana tare da glycoproteins na surface da kuma nucleocapsid proteins suna samar da vesicles dauke da virions, wanda daga bisani ya haɗu da membrane plasma don saki kwayar cutar.
An ba da rahoton farkon tsarin halittar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 10 ga Janairu, 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 an gano cewa sabon nau'in beta-CoV ne tare da fiye da kashi 99.98% na asalin kwayoyin halitta a cikin samfuran 10 da aka tattara daga asalin cutar, Kasuwar Abinci ta Kifi ta Huanan a Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da SARS-CoV fiye da MERS-CoV.
Ta hanyar microscope na lantarki, an gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin mafi ƙanƙantar ɓangaren ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum.
An gano ACE2 na ɗan adam a matsayin mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da ACE2 cikin rauni fiye da SARS-CoV, wanda ya dace da gaskiyar cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta a cikin marasa lafiya fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samar da sabbin furotin masu sauƙi waɗanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf3b da furotin da aka ɓoye wanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf8.
orf3b don SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa a cikin cutar kwayar cutar kuma yana da bayanin IFNβ; duk da haka, orf8 ba ya ƙunshe da kowane yanki ko dalili mai aiki.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairun 2020, Zhou, et al., sun ba da rahoton cewa tsarin cyro-EM na ACE2 na ɗan adam gaba ɗaya yana da ƙuduri na 2.9 Å a cikin hadaddun tare da jigilar amino acid B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa hadaddun, waɗanda ke da buɗewa da rufewa, an haɗa su azaman dimers kuma hadaddun ACE-BOAT2 na iya haɗa sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke ba da hujja don ganowa da kamuwa da CoV.
B0AT1 na iya zama maƙasudin magani don tace magunguna don hana kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2.
Tushen asali da na tsakiya
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS Cov sun samo asali ne daga barbashi kuma an watsa su ga mutane ta hanyar fox da raƙumi.
Ta hanyar kwatanta tsarin halittar SARS-CoV-2 da sauran CoVs, ana ganin cewa barbashi ne asalin SARS-CoV-2 saboda sabon kwayar cutar tana da kamanni 96% da SARS-like CoVs biyu daga barbashi da ake kira bat-SL-CoVZX45 da bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Koyaya, matsakaicin mai watsa shiri wanda ke taimaka wa ƙwayoyin cuta su ƙetare shingen jinsin don kamuwa da mutane ya kasance ba a sani ba, kuma har yanzu ba a bayyana hanyar watsawa ba.
Ji, et al., sun ba da shawarar maciji a matsayin mai ɗaukar hoto na kwayar cutar daga bargo zuwa mutum wanda ya shafi sake haɗuwa da homolog a cikin furotin S.
