Duk da haka, bambancin 1% da ke yadawa a cikin dukkanin kwayoyin halitta biyu har yanzu yana da bambanci mai yawa; saboda haka, an jira sakamakon ƙarshe don tattara hujjoji masu mahimmanci (Fig.33).
