Cutar zazzabi yawanci ita ce babban alamun farko na COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa ba tare da wata alama ba ko wasu alamun kamar bushewar tari, numfashi, ciwon tsoka, jiri, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna fama da dyspnea da / ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan farawar cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, yanayin mai haƙuri yana ci gaba da hanzari zuwa ciwon huhu mai tsanani, ƙwayoyin cuta, acidosis na metabolic da coagulopathy.
Marasa lafiya da ke fama da zazzabi da/ko cututtukan numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani, koda ba tare da wani abu ba na hoto na huhu, ya kamata a bincika su don cutar don ganewar asali.
Binciken alƙaluma a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa yawan alamun cutar shine 98% don zazzabi, 76% don bushewar tari, 55% don dyspnea, da 3% don zawo; 8% na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon numfashi.
