Ana amfani da steroids, a matsayin masu hana rigakafi, a cikin maganin SARS don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
Koyaya, steroids a manyan allurai ba su da fa'ida ga mummunan raunin huhu a cikin marasa lafiya SARS da COVID-19.
A gefe guda, steroids a cikin manyan allurai na iya haifar da mummunan sakamako masu illa, musamman osteonecrosis avascular, yana shafar hangen nesa sosai.
Koyaya, an ba da shawarar amfani da ƙananan allurai na ƙananan ƙwayar cuta na ɗan gajeren lokaci tare da taka tsantsan ga marasa lafiya masu cutar COVID-19.
A lokacin da aka rubuta wannan labarin, babu maganin rigakafi mai tasiri da aka tabbatar.
Koyaya, amfani da allurar cikin jijiya tare da remdesivir, analog na nucleotide, an same shi da tasiri a kan wani mai cutar Amurka mai cutar COVID-19.
Remdesivir wani magani ne na rigakafin cutar da Gilead ta fara samarwa don magance cututtukan da cutar Ebola da Marlburg ke haifarwa.
Daga baya, remdesivir ya kuma nuna yiwuwar hana sauran ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA guda ɗaya ciki har da MERS da SARS.
