A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19  cuta da ke haifar da coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  a matsayin annoba.
Duk da cewa kalmar "annoba" tana nufin kawai yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda hatsarin wani lamari yake ba, WHO ta fahimci bukatar da ake da ita na tilasta wa gwamnatoci su dauki mataki:
Dukkan kasashen duniya na iya canza yanayin annobar.
Idan kasashe suka gano, gwada, kula, killace, sa ido da kuma motsa al'ummarsu su dauki mataki, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna matukar damuwa game da duka matakan kamuwa da cutar da kuma mummunan aiki da kuma rashin aiki.
A cewar Dokta Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amurka, annobar "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
Ya ce, a cikin wani bayani da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, "ban da mura, ba a gano wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na numfashi ba daga fitowarsu zuwa ci gaba da yaduwa a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya bayyana irin wannan ra'ayi, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da cutar coronavirus ta haifar ba".
Ya ci gaba, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin annoba da za a iya sarrafa ta a lokaci guda ba".
Sabon matsayin cutar ya biyo bayan shawarar da WHO ta yanke a watan Janairu don ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a a duniya.
