Alamun COVID-19 na iya zama marasa ƙayyadaddun kuma mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar na iya zama marasa alamun cutar.
Alamun biyu da suka fi yawa sune zazzabi (88%) da bushewar tari (68%).
