Binciken kwayoyin halitta ya nuna cewa coronavirus yana da nasaba da kwayoyin halitta tare da Betacoronavirus, a cikin Sarbecovirus subgenus (B-domain) tare da zaren biyu da aka samo daga bat.
Kwayar cutar ta kasance daidai da kashi 96% a matakin cikakken kwayar halitta tare da samfurin sauran coronavirus na bat (BatCov RaTG13).
A watan Fabrairun 2020, masu bincike na kasar Sin sun gano cewa akwai bambanci kawai na amino acid a wasu sassan tsarin kwayoyin halittar mutum tsakanin kwayar cutar daga lard da kwayar cutar daga mutum.
Bambancin kwayoyin halittar mutum har zuwa yanzu ya gano cewa a mafi yawan kashi 92% na kwayoyin halitta sun kasance tsakanin coronavirus na shingles da SARS-CoV-2, wanda bai isa ya tabbatar da shingles a matsayin matsakaiciyar matsakaici ba.
Ana iya gano kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar cutar ta hanyar alamun cututtuka, kodayake a ƙarshe ana tabbatar da shi ta hanyar sake fasalin maganin polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) na ɓoyewar kamuwa da cutar ko CT imaging.
Wani binciken da ya kwatanta PCR da CT a Wuhan ya ba da shawarar cewa CT ya fi ƙarfin PCR, kodayake ba shi da ƙwarewa, tare da yawancin siffofin hoton da ke kan gaba tare da cutar huhu da sauran cututtuka.
Har zuwa Maris 2020, Kwalejin Radiology ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar cewa "bai kamata a yi amfani da CT don tantancewa ko azaman gwajin farko don gano COVID-19 ba".
WHO ta wallafa wasu takaddun shaida na gwajin RNA don SARS-CoV-1, tare da na farko da aka fitar a ranar 17 ga Janairu.
Gwajin yana amfani da ainihin lokacin sake fasalin tsarin polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR).
Ana iya yin wannan gwajin a kan numfashi ko jini.
Sakamakon gwajin yana samuwa a cikin sa'o'i da dama zuwa kwanaki.
Yawancin lokaci ana yin gwajin ne da swabs na nasopharyngeal amma ana iya amfani da swabs na pharynx. Yawancin dakunan gwaje-gwaje da kamfanoni suna haɓaka gwajin serology, wanda ke gano ƙwayoyin cuta.
Har zuwa 6 ga Afrilu 2020, babu ɗayan waɗannan gwaje-gwajen da aka tabbatar da cewa sun isa sosai don amincewa da amfani da su sosai.
A Amurka gwajin ƙwayar cuta wanda Cellex ya haɓaka an yarda da shi don amfani da gaggawa ta hanyar dakunan gwaje-gwaje masu izini kawai.
