Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa marasa lafiya da za a shigar da su a keɓe su zuwa wuraren jira daban-daban dangane da ko sun kasance masu cutar COVID-19 da ake zargi. Baya ga PPE, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu yin aiki a nisan ƙafa 6 daga marasa lafiya da aka sani, ko ake zargi, da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da waɗanda ke yin aikin samar da aerosol.
A cikin Amurka, N95 mai tace fuska mai numfashi wanda aka amince da NIOSH ko mafi kyau dole ne a yi amfani dashi a cikin mahallin cikakken tsari da rubutaccen shirin kariya na numfashi wanda ya haɗa da gwajin dacewa, horo da gwajin likita.
Sauran nau'ikan na'urorin numfashi na iya ba da kariya mafi girma da haɓaka jin daɗin ma'aikata. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar suturar rufewa ba saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi wacce ba ta yaduwa ta ruwa na jiki.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata kawai ga ma'aikatan da ke kula da shiga da fita.
Ga waɗanda ke karɓar samfurin numfashi daga, kula da, ko jigilar marasa lafiya na COVID-19 ba tare da hanyoyin samar da aerosol ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rufe fuska, fuska, ko idanu, rigunan kariya da safar hannu.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, ana maye gurbin abin rufe fuska da N95 ko respirator FFP2.
Ganin cewa samar da PPE a duniya bai isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatun PPE ta hanyar telehealth, shinge na zahiri kamar taga mai haske, ta hanyar ba da damar waɗanda ke cikin kulawa ta kai tsaye don shiga ɗakin marasa lafiya na COVID-19, ta amfani da PPE kawai da ake buƙata don takamaiman ayyuka, ci gaba da amfani da kayan numfashi iri ɗaya ba tare da cire su ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali iri ɗaya, saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da PPE, da kuma hana amfani da abin rufe fuska ga mutane marasa alamun cutar.
