Aikace-aikacen b'COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu wanda aka tsara don taimakawa bin hanyar tuntuɓar mutum a cikin martani ga cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, wanda shine tsarin gano mutanen ("abokan hulɗa") waɗanda zasu iya kasancewa tare da mutum mai kamuwa da cuta.
Mutane da yawa aikace-aikace da aka ɓullo da ko samarwa da gwamnatin jami'an goyon bayan a wasu yankuna da kuma jurisdictions.
An samar da wasu tsarin don gina aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba.
An haifar da damuwa game da sirri, musamman game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin yanayin aikace-aikacen masu amfani.
Sauran hanyoyin da ba su da damuwa sun haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar kusanci ga mai amfani a kan sauran wayoyin salula.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar cewa za su haɗa aikin don tallafawa aikace-aikacen tushen Bluetooth kai tsaye cikin tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin, tare da haɗin gwiwar Alipay, ta ƙaddamar da wata manhaja da ke ba 'yan ƙasa damar bincika ko sun taɓa yin hulɗa da waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane sama da 200 a kasar Sin. A Singapore, ana amfani da wata manhaja da ake kira TraceTogether.
An haɓaka aikace-aikacen ta hanyar ƙungiyar IT ta gida, an ƙaddamar da shi azaman tushen buɗewa kuma za a ba da shi ga gwamnati.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka haɓaka aikace-aikacen.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran amincewa ta Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta bayyana cewa aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana cikin matakan ci gaba, kuma zai kasance a shirye don ƙaddamarwa a cikin 'yan makonni.
Australia da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da ke kan aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na da niyyar gabatar da aikace-aikacen ƙuntatawa na ƙasa don marasa lafiya da aka gano da COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow, waɗanda aka tsara don tabbatar da cewa ba su bar gida ba.
Ross Anderson, farfesa a fannin tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge, ya lissafa wasu matsaloli masu amfani da tsarin aikace-aikacen aikace-aikace, ciki har da kuskuren kuskure da kuma yiwuwar rashin tasiri idan aiwatar da aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙananan yawan jama'a.
Dangane da damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu rikitarwa ko haɗari, Apple ya sanya iyaka ga nau'ikan ƙungiyoyi waɗanda za su iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da suka shafi coronavirus a cikin App Store, suna iyakance su ga "masu iko" ko kuma manyan ƙungiyoyi kawai.
Google da Amazon sun sanya irin wannan takunkumin.
Masu fafutukar kare sirrin sun nuna damuwarsu game da tasirin sa ido kan amfani da aikace-aikacen coronavirus, musamman game da ko za a dakatar da tsarin sa ido da aka kirkira don magance cutar coronavirus da zarar barazanar ta wuce.
Amnesty International da wasu kungiyoyi sama da 100 sun fitar da wata sanarwa da ke kira da a kawo karshen irin wannan sa ido.
Kungiyar ta bayyana sharudda takwas ga ayyukan gwamnati:
Dole ne a yi amfani da "daidai da doka, idan ya cancanta kuma ya dace";
Za a iya samun ƙarin kulawa da kulawa tare da sassan da aka saka;
amfani da bayanai ya kamata ya kasance iyakance ga manufar COVID-19;
Ana buƙatar a tabbatar da tsaro da kuma rashin sani na bayanai da aka tabbatar da cewa an tabbatar da su;
Dole ne a hana kulawar dijital daga ƙara tsanantawa da nuna bambanci da ɓoyewa;
Duk wani musayar bayanai tare da wasu kamfanoni dole ne a bayyana su a cikin doka;
Za a kare su daga cin zarafi da kuma hakkin 'yan kasa na mayar da martani kan cin zarafi;
Za a buƙaci a sami ma'ana ta hanyar duk "masu ruwa da tsaki", gami da masana kiwon lafiya da kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu.
Shawarwarin shirin Google/Apple suna nufin magance matsalar sa ido ta yau da kullun ta hanyar cire hanyoyin sa ido daga tsarin aiki na na'urorin su da zarar ba a buƙatar su.
Wasu ƙasashe suna amfani da bin sawun wurin da ke kan hanyar sadarwa maimakon aikace-aikace, kawar da buƙatun duka biyu don saukar da aikace-aikacen da ikon kauce wa sa ido.
A Isra'ila, an yarda da bin sawun yanar gizo.
Hanyoyin sadarwa masu amfani da hanyar sadarwa waɗanda ke da damar yin amfani da bayanan wuri na asali suna da babbar matsala game da sirrin sirri.
Koyaya, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabar cibiyar sadarwa bane dole ne su sami damar yin amfani da bayanan wurin zama na sirri; an riga an ƙirƙiri wasu tsarin kiyaye sirrin sirri waɗanda ke amfani da sabar cibiyar sadarwa kawai don sadarwa tare da juna (duba sashe na ƙasa).
A Koriya ta Kudu, ana amfani da tsarin da aka yi amfani da shi don yin amfani da hanyar sadarwa.
Maimakon amfani da aikace-aikacen da aka keɓance, tsarin yana tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban-daban ciki har da bayanan sa ido na na'urar hannu da bayanan ma'amala na katin, kuma haɗuwa da waɗannan duka yana haifar da sanarwa ta hanyar saƙon rubutu ga mutanen da ke iya kamuwa da cutar.
Baya ga amfani da wannan bayanin don faɗakar da masu yuwuwar tuntuɓar, gwamnati ta kuma ba da bayanan wurin ga jama'a, wani abu da aka ba da izini saboda manyan canje-canje a cikin dokokin sirrin bayanai bayan barkewar cutar MERS a ƙasar.
Ana samun wannan bayanin ga jama'a ta hanyar wasu aikace-aikace da shafukan yanar gizo.
Har zuwa 6 ga Afrilu 2020, ba a ba da cikakken bayani ba.
Kula da alaƙa da kiyaye sirrin sirri ra'ayi ne da aka tsara tare da mahimman littattafan nazarin jiki tun daga 2013.
Duk da haka, PEPP-PT aiki ne na daidaituwa wanda ya ƙunshi matsakaiciyar hanya da tsakiya, kuma ba yarjejeniya guda ɗaya ba.
A cikin wannan yarjejeniya, bayanan da aka gano da kansu ba su taɓa barin na'urar ba, kuma duk haɗuwa tana faruwa akan na'urar.
Kungiyar Sirrin MIT Media Lab tana haɓaka SafePaths, dandamali don amfani da fasahohin tsare sirri lokacin tattarawa da amfani da wuri ko bayanan haɗin gwiwa don bin hanyar COVID-19.
Wannan ya dogara ne akan bincike daga takardar farin takarda "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" da aka buga a watan Maris na 2020. Wani irin wannan yunƙuri shine dandamali na SafeTrace ta Enigma MPC, wani kamfani mai haɓaka fasahar sirri wanda kuma aka kafa asali a MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace yana amfani da fasahar kayan aiki mai aminci don bawa masu amfani damar raba wuri mai mahimmanci da bayanan kiwon lafiya tare da sauran masu amfani da hukumomi, ba tare da yin sulhu kan sirrin bayanai ba.
A ranar 5 ga Afrilu, 2020, an kafa ƙungiyar TCN Coalition ta duniya ta ƙungiyoyi da yawa waɗanda suka haɗu kan mahimman hanyoyin da manyan ladabi masu yawa, tare da manufar rage rarrabuwa, da kuma ba da damar aiki a duniya ta hanyar aikace-aikacen sa ido da faɗakarwa, muhimman fannoni don cimma amfani da yawa.
A ranar 9 ga Afrilu 2020, gwamnatin Singapore ta sanar da cewa ta buɗe tushen yarjejeniyar BlueTrace da aikace-aikacen gwamnati na hukuma ke amfani da ita.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple, kamfanonin da ke sarrafa dandamali na Android da iOS, sun sanar da wani shiri don bin hanyoyin sadarwa wanda suke da'awar zai kiyaye sirrin su, bisa ga haɗin haɗin Bluetooth Low Power da kuma sirrin sirri.
Sun kuma buga takamaiman fasahar da ake amfani da ita a cikin tsarin.
